ased by 2 points per &lt;br/&gt;turn. In exchange, the player will have to pay 10% of &lt;br/&gt;the cost of the unit.&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:8pt; font-weight:600; color:#ffffff;&quot;&gt;Fusion&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:8pt; color:#ffffff;&quot;&gt;: Two units of the same type whose life is &lt;br/&gt;smaller than 10 can merge.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:8pt; color:#ffffff;&quot;&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:8pt; color:#ffffff;&quot;&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:8pt; color:#ffffff;&quot;&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:8pt; color:#ffffff;&quot;&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/body&gt;&lt;/html&gt;</string>
